text: A golden opportunity! 1st time on the market for this rare, 5 acre tract on in the Pleasant Ridge area just outside La Conner! This heavily timbered property is perfect for your private estate in the woods!

Bring your plans and build! This breathtaking 4.6 acre property nestled in the mountains is ready to bring your vision to life. This level, cleared lot offers you the tranquility of living among the wildlife. Close to Marblemounts rural amenities and all the outdoor activities the Cascades and Skagit River can offer. Power in the street. Welcome to your nature getaway!

Welcome to your own forest oasis with a custom-built Spane home & 36x42 detached shop! Built in 2014, this exquisite home features open main living with 20+ft tall ceilings, cement floors, air-conditioning, HUGE covered wrap-around patio, quality wood trim & doors, and large en-suite primary bed on the main floor. Upstairs loft has full bath & potential for 3rd bed/bonus room. The fully fenced property offers the privacy and tranquility you're looking for, w/ 500' of riverfront (no flood risk to home) & hundreds of acres of wooded forest w/ access to hiking or nature walks right out your backdoor. Shop has 3 extra-deep bays w/ a finished room on 2nd floor & large lean-to on the side for boat/RV parking, and home has extra carport parking.

Lovely NW craftsman style cottage home in the beautiful J Avenue Cottages community, a quaint neighborhood that offers pride of ownership and turn key living! This gorgeous home offers main level living, custom woodwork, maple hardwood flooring, vaulted ceilings, & a spacious kitchen with granite counters & stainless appliances. The cozy gas fireplace is perfect for those chilly winter evenings! Spacious primary suite with ensuite bath & walk-in closet. Upstairs has a wonderful sunny loft with views of Mount Baker & Fidalgo bay plus an extra bedroom & full bath for guests. The loft makes a perfect extra family room & office space. Newer ductless mini split heat pump provides A/C on those warmer summer days. Superb in town location!!!

Adorable country rambler located in the area of Lyman! Walk through the front door & you are welcomed into the livingroom which features a cozy pellet stove. A dining area can be found as well with a sliding glass door leading to a covered back deck. Two bedrooms & a full bathroom are on one end of the home while the kitchen sits on the other. A bonus room with a wood burning fireplace can be found beside the kitchen which can be used as an office or bedroom if desired. Large laundry room also with access to the garage! Head outside to a spacious back yard complete with a covered patio, chicken coop, & seasonal creek with a bridge! There is a large shop right next to the home, offering ample storage & space for hobbies. Come call it home!

Welcome to your dream retreat! Nestled in the heart of the countryside, this expansive property offers over 8 acres of serene landscape, perfect for those seeking a peaceful lifestyle away from the hustle and bustle of city life. This charming residence boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, a spacious kitchen and wonderful wrap around trex deck taking in all the territorial views.Enjoy the established garden space and fruit trees offering the perfect opportunity to harvest your own produce or grow the flower garden of your dreams. For the DIY enthusiast or hobbyist, a massive 30X60 shop awaits! This versatile space is ideal for storing equipment, pursuing projects or even setting up a business - the possibilities are endless. Pre-inspected!

Welcome to the Beale's Maple Grove neighborhood. This 1823 sq. ft. single level 3 bedroom, 2 bath home boasts an updated kitchen, a spacious living rm. LVP floors, vaulted ceilings & awesome views! The primary bathroom is a true retreat, w/ modern finishes & huge shower! Attached 2+ Garage w/ work space, gives plenty of room for vehicles & hobbies. Solar panels & an on-demand hot water heater, energy efficient windows & doors keep the costs down. Enjoy the deck & fully fenced backyard & soak in the views of Mt. Baker, Guemes , Saddleback islands & the Sound. Cozy fire pit to watch the sunsets. Close to Parks, Golf Course, Marina, grocery, hardware, specialty shops, & an array of restaurants .Don't miss your chance to own this unique home!
nearby_schools: Anacortes School District, Northwest Educational Service District 189

text: Welcome to this nicely updated Creekside home! Hardwood floors throughout except bedrooms, kitchen and baths. New gas fireplace in 2019 (no pilot needed, remote control), custom window coverings, new windows and slider. Some newer appliances plus washer and dryer. New a/c in 2022. Lots of windows to enjoy a great view of Mount Baker. RV parking onsite. Nice deck off slider. This home has been very well taken care of and is move in ready!

One level living at the end of a quiet, dead-end road, across the street from the waterfront. FEE SIMPLE ownership, not leased land. Relax on the deck & enjoy the peaceful, sunset views of Skagit Bay. This updated home has a warm, cabin like feel with hardwood floors, wood wrapped windows, vaulted ceiling, & cozy woodstove. Huge primary bedroom could be divided to create a 3rd BR. New roof, carpet, & tile. 36' x 24' shop / garage has a single door but a 3 car width. Extra area off primary can be used as office. Private setting with large yard area & plenty of parking for boat or RV. Hydronic baseboard heat. Enjoy an easy Pacific Northwest lifestyle, close to the fun of La Conner & Anacortes. Pre inspection report is available. What a find!

Brand new manufactured home on 1.9 acres close to the Skagit River, Sauk Mountain, and hiking trails (Rockport State Park, Sauk Mountain, and Howard Miller Park). Across the road, you can launch your boat at Howard Miller Park. Property has Full RV hookups plus an APPROVED PERMIT to build a 24 x 36 Shop next to the house. Nice setting with woods surrounding you. Only 35 minutes to Sedro Woolley.

Lovely rambler in the Meadows featuring 3beds & 1.5baths! Optimal open-concept living space, complete w/ central A/C & double pane windows. The kitchen is equipped with newer stainless & black appliances. Enjoy your primary bedroom w/ ensuite bath, spacious laundry room, and a large 2-car garage w/ a workshop area. Enjoy your brand new roof & a fully fenced backyard w/ a custom poured patio, a garden area ready for your personal touch, flower beds, covered pergola for BBQs, & a sizable shed/shop w/ storage above. Situated on a corner lot in a cul-de-sac offering privacy within a wonderful neighborhood that includes a neighborhood park. Owners also have access to a large paved community parking area for RVs, boats, or trailers.

text: Delightful Rambler just waiting for its new owner. Situated back off the road on an oversized lot, you will appreciate some of the upgrades to this home. Covered front porch welcomes you inside to an open floor plan offering vaulted ceilings, updated lighting & laminate flooring thru out much of the main living areas. Kitchen w/ newer stainless appliances ~ breakfast bar, walk in pantry, ample cabinets & great counterspace. Spacious primary bedroom w/ 3/4 bath & double closets. 2 guest bdrms & full bath complete this one level living. Awesome deck w/ steps to the fully fenced back yard w/ garden shed, great lawn areas & corner water feature. Attached single care garage & RV parking as well as ample guest parking. Don't miss this one.

text: Cozy and updated 2 bedroom, 1.5 bath Northridge condo awaits! Featuring a light-filled entryway with skylight, the efficient layout includes a completely updated half-bath on the main, living/dining space with standalone gas stove, a kitchen updated with butcher block countertops and tile backsplash, and a slider to a sweet little fenced yard space with patio and no-maintenance turf. Upper floor features a full bath and two bedrooms - one with its own private deck, perfect for your morning coffee or yoga session. Convenient extra storage in the carport. HOA dues cover exterior maintenance (building is freshly painted!), Comcast internet and cable, W/S/G. Ditch the gym for the clubhouse with sport court, indoor pool, sauna, and more!

text: Perched on Buchanan Hill, this single story home offers incredible unobstructed views of the Skagit Valley and Mountains beyond! Step inside to an open living space w/ hardwood floors and gas fireplace. Kitchen has ample cabinet and counter space and an island eating area. Three bedrooms including Primary w/ private en-suite bath and walk in closet. Efficient Heat pump warms or cools the home as needed. Wrap-around covered porch and the back deck is the perfect place to take in those views. Two car garage. Situated on a desirable 1.52 acre lot. Seller offering a $10k credit in lieu of carpet/paint towards buyers closing costs w/ full price offer. 1.52 acre vacant lot next door also for sale MLS# 2297823. You will not want to miss this one!
